properties.property: Do not listen to the one on the left! I am right and I say when you see a path leading left you go there and not to the right The lever there will certainly help you
That fool on the right, he doensn't know what he's saying. When you see a road leading to right, head straight there! Only bad things will happen at the path to the left.
Do you not see? The left is a fool! Continue to trust me and hear what I say, look for the lever hidden between chiseled stone! When you flip it you'll feel the ground shake and the exit open up!
I know I was wrong, but that switch that you flipped, it's shown me the path! Search for the button in between cliffs. Press it and the path to the exit shall open!
I was right as you see, so would you trust once again? I say you should search all along the bottom path. There what you find will aid in your goal.
I was wrong, an honest mistake! Trust me this time would you please? Go through the top path and check everywhere! Hidden somewhere you'll find what you seek!
I may have been wrong for two times by now, but that shake, that lever has given advice. I say you should go to the right this time. There under a rock you will find a secret that helps.

property.name: text
property.value: As you see, the right is a fool! Twice now he's proven! Trust me yet again and go to the left, and find what you want under a rock.

properties.property: I was sadly mistaken, but this time I'm sure! Look along the cliffs as much as you can, as there's something hidden here somewhere. And avoid the cliffs with what looks like dead bush, that is where the rock-bats nest!

After my succes would you believe me this time? I say there is nothing here for you to find, so move on quickly and stay alive. There are dangerous bats nesting among these rocks, beware the cliffs with what looks like a withered plant!
The left is quite dense, what shake is he saying? I know for sure one thing that the button is hidden in rocks not made nests! So stay far from those bats and look for what you need.
I've felt it again! That shake in the earth has shown me the answer. That what you seek is near those bat nests below. Be careful however, they'll surely attack when you approach their homes!
